# =============================================================================
# Agent Inc. Public SOL Facilitator
# =============================================================================
# We offer our native SOL facilitator as a public service for other x402 apps.
# External developers can use our facilitator URL in their x402 integrations.
#
# Public Facilitator URL: https://agentinc.fun/api/x402/facilitator
#
# Endpoints:
#   GET  /                - Facilitator info and documentation
#   GET  /supported       - Supported networks (solana, solana-devnet)
#   GET  /price?usd=0.01  - Convert USD to SOL/lamports at current rate
#   POST /verify          - Verify a payment transaction
#   POST /settle          - Submit and confirm payment on-chain
#
# Features:
#   - Native SOL payments (no USDC or wrapped tokens)
#   - Live USD to SOL conversion via Jupiter/CoinGecko
#   - Works on mainnet and devnet
#   - Compatible with x402 protocol standard